item.title: Project 4: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) and Data Cleaning of Spark Fund Investments
item.description: This project deals with the Exploratory Data Analysis and the Data Cleaning of the various Companies Data for Spark Fund Investment, along with the Profiling Report. A detailed HTML version of the profiling reports for the Companies Data and the Rounds Data can be viewed from the reports folder of the project’s github repository. NOTE: HTML Reports can be accessed in a user-friendly readable format via a web browser; after copying it into a local folder of the desktop/laptop.
